OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening. Then the rest of
OL,7,Fthe night will be mainly dry with
OL,8,Fclear periods and just the odd shower.
OL,9,FCold with frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMainly dry in the morning.
OL,12,FOutbreaks of rain and high ground snow
OL,13,Fspreading east during the afternoon
OL,14,Fand evening. Winds strengthening for a
OL,15,Ftime in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
