OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain,
OL,6,Fhill snow clearing east on Friday
OL,7,Fmorning, otherwise cloudy with
OL,8,Fshowers, wintry on hills. Rain and
OL,9,Fhill snow spreading northeast on
OL,10,FSaturday. Wintry showers on Sunday.
OL,11,FSevere gales possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
